 advanced personnel air cargo aviation checkpoint checked baggage and critical infrastructure screening as well as cargo and border security applications the company offers its products through a sales and distribution network in the united states and internationally the company was incorporated in  and is headquartered in woburn massachusetts with additional offices in the united kingdom singapore the united arab emirates china and australia l communications security and detection systems inc operates as a subsidiary of l communications holdings inc detailed description e commerce waywoburn ma united statesfounded in  employees phone  fax  wwwsdslcomcom key executives for l communications security and detection systems inc mr thomas m ripp president omer khan founder mr william j frain chief financial officer and treasurer mr daniel j silva vice president of operations paul simpson senior director of cargo product line compensation as of fiscal year  l communications security and detection systems inc key developments l communications security  detection systems inc wins  federal contract mar   l communications security  detection systems inc won a  federal contract from the us department of homeland securitys transportation security administration for alarm signal and security detection equipment for the charleston international airport south carolina l communications security  detection systems inc wins  million federal contract mar   l communications security  detection systems inc won a  federal contract from the us department of homeland securitys transportation security administration for alarm signal and security detection equipment vivid technologies appoints freddie achom as nonexecutive chairman sep   vivid technologies has named freddie achom as its new nonexecutive chairman as part of the companys plans to expand into the middle east telecoms sector and other developing markets achom has been brought on to advise founder omer khan and the vivid board th