twork  the only vetted password protected career networking platform designed exclusively for securitycleared professionals   our team meet the team behind clearancejobs the largest career network dedicated to matching securitycleared candidates to government defense and intelligence companies   who uses clearancejobs clearancejobs is used by over a thousand defense and intelligence contractors like northrop grumman booz allen raytheon general dynamics rand as well as federal government agencies including the cia fbi federal reserve and national laboratories   a word on security safety security and privacy are critical priorities for securitycleared professionals and clearancejobs takes that seriously clearancejobs is protected using the same encryption software that banks use we are the only career network with endtoend https traffic encryption    clearancejobs all rights reserved clearancejobs is a dhi service cleared candidate registration  clearancejobs already have an account login here security clearance verification please check the following statements that apply to you i have had a job in the past two years that required use of a clearance i currently have an active or current clearance i am a us citizen you meet the requirements to register for a clearancejobs account click register to continue all jobs and opportunities on clearancejobscom require an active or current clearance cancel register candidate registration user information all fields are required to register on clearancejobs username your username can only contain letters and numbers email password your password must contain a letter a number and a special character and must be between    characters my clearance level please selectunspecifieddoe q or ldept of homeland securitypublic trustconfidentialsecrettop secrettop secretsciintel agency nsa cia fbi etc back continue candidate registration contact information all fields are required to register on clearancejobs first name last name street add